{"lemma":"خَسِيسَةٍ","slug":"خَسِيسَةٍ","root":"خ.س.س","root_slug":"خ-س-س","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-س-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10581"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"low, vile, contemptible"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"low in quantity"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb خَسَّ (ḵassa)."},"ipa":["/xa.siːs/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10581","headword_ar":"خَسِيسَةٌ","root":"xs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasiysN","text_ar":"خَسِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b2-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEa A@ll~`hu xasiysapa fulaAnK","text_ar":"رَفَعَ ا@للّٰهُ خَسِيسَةَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God raised the condition of such a one after it had been low:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEotu mino xasiysatihi","text_ar":"رَفَعْتُ مِنْ خَسِيسَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did to him a deed whereby he became raised to a high condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"within the period of the shedding of the central incisors:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAwazati Aln~aAqapu xasiysatahaA","text_ar":"جَاوَزَتِ النَّاقَةُ خَسِيسَتَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel passed beyond"},{"kind":"text","text":"the period of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasiysap","text_ar":"خَسِيسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: this is in the sixth year, when she sheds her central incisor: she is then such as is allowable for sacrifice. (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["Az","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}